3/16 The Little Mermaid has five sisters, and her grandmother is a queen who wears ‘twelve oyster tails on her tail, whereas the highest of the nobles were allowed to wear only six’ (50). #DigiChildLit #childrensbooks #kidlit #littlemermaid #TheLittleMermaid
